            <li><a target="_blank" href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/enable-and-disable-cookies-website-preferences" style="text-decoration: underline; color: blue">Cookie settings in Firefox</a></li>
            <li><a target="_blank" href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647?co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop&hl=en" style="text-decoration: underline; color: blue">Cookie settings in Chrome</a></li>
            <li><a target="_blank" href="https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-and-website-data-sfri11471/mac" style="text-decoration: underline; color: blue">Cookie settings in Cookie settings in Safari web and iOS</a></li>
        </ul>
    </p>
